('junior', 'The letter ___ personally by the CEO.', '["A. writes", "B. was written", "C. wrote", "D. writing"]'::jsonb, 'B', 1, '信被撰寫／簽署語境用被動。'),
('junior', 'She ___ her ankle while jogging.', '["A. breaks", "B. broke", "C. was breaking", "D. has broken"]'::jsonb, 'B', 1, '慢跑時扭傷，過去式 broke。'),
