('college', 'The instrument demonstrates adequate ___.', '["A. reliable", "B. reliability", "C. reliably", "D. relying"]'::jsonb, 'B', 1, '名詞 reliability 十足。'),
('college', 'Cronbach''s alpha reflects internal ___.', '["A. consistent", "B. consistency", "C. consistently", "D. consistor"]'::jsonb, 'B', 1, '內部一致性 consistency。'),
